data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT RequestDate, TrainingCourse, TrainingType, NumOfEmpJoin, TrainerName, RequestCode, Locations, RequesterName, TRH.Remark, FromDate, ToDate, ApproverCode, ApproverName, ApprovedDate, HRD.Description as Department, HRB.Description as Branch FROM TrainingRequestHeader TRH left join HRStaffProfile ST on ST.EmpCode = TRH.RequestCode left join HRDepartment HRD on HRD.Code = ST.DEPT left join HRBranch HRB on HRB.Code = ST.Branch where TRH.ID= @ID
